<HEADLINE>
<P>
CYPRESS' WORKS SCORES RECORD 45 POINTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Sara Works broke her single-game school record by scoring 45 points in 
Cypress' 71-49 quarterfinal victory over American River Wednesday in the 
Fullerton tournament. 
</P>
<P>
 The sophomore from Savanna High, who averages a state-leading 28 points, made 
17 of 27 from the field and 11 of 13 from the line to better by three points 
the record she set earlier this season. 
</P>
