 Texas Tech linebacker Zach Thomas on his team's record: 
</P>
<P>
 "Some people think we don't need to go to a bowl with a 6-5 record. It's not a 
good record. I didn't want to go with it, either. I wanted to go to the Cotton 
Bowl, but I didn't want to be 6-5.  
</P>
<P>
 "I think the Lord blessed us by putting us in this position by putting (Texas) 
A&M on probation. A&M, they cheated so they deserved to be put on probation." 
EARL GUSTKEY 
