 Reseda High center Akua Floyd was dismissed from the boys' basketball team 
Wednesday prior to the Regents' Birmingham tournament game against Van Nuys, 
Coach David Enowitz said. 
</P>
<P>
 Enowitz cited "repeated disciplinary problems" for the dismissal of the 
