</P>
<P>
 Duly Noted: Paloma Picasso's signature red lipstick is missing from her new 
ads for Tiffany . . . Super-model Kristen McMenamy's gone strawberry blond . . 
. Westside pigeons have a new favorite perch -- Bijan's giant billboard head at 
Veteran Avenue and Santa Monica Boulevard. 
</P>
